0080\\u0099s father\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"lifelong coach\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cCould be the end for a shot-putter.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"a shot-putter\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your pec is directly connected to the movement.\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your pec\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"the movement\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just devastating.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The muscle tear was on top of an injury to the ulnar nerve in his throwing elbow he suffered at the world indoor championships in Glasgow on March 1.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.8791148402900881, \"rank\": 0.13743626140857046, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The muscle tear\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the ulnar nerve\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"his throwing elbow\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"the world indoor championships\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s elbow began hurting long before then.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s elbow\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, his nerve had swelled tofive timesits normal size, causing severe pain.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"his nerve\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"tofive timesits normal size\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"severe pain\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was cubital tunnel syndrome, which feels like hitting your funny bone over and over.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cubital tunnel syndrome\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"your funny bone\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan called the combination of the muscle tear and the elbow injury \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cuncomfortable.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d A mere mortal might call it \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cdebilitating.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Ryan had been addressing the sore elbow with treatment and physical therapy.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550643055, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550637088, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the combination\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscle tear\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"the elbow injury\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the sore elbow\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"treatment\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"physical therapy\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after tearing the pec, he abandoned the tweak-and-adapt approach.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pec\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"the tweak-and-adapt approach\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had an ultrasound procedure, a nerve hydrodissection, to propel the nerve out of its groove with a saline solution.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ultrasound procedure\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"a nerve hydrodissection\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"the nerve\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"its groove\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"a saline solution\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nerve could then be freed from everything else (muscles, tissue, etc.).\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The nerve\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"muscles\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"tissue\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even after tearing the pec, Ryan still trained as much as he could.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1677, \"end\": 1681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550637088, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pec\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He just couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t throw\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094formonths.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t throw\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094formonths\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As trials drew near, in late June, neither Ryan nor Mitch had any real idea if Ryan could even qualify for Paris.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1798, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550637088, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999999469117725, \"rank\": 4.9506213844482536e-08, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550637088, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1862, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9988458239523611, \"rank\": 0.00115550970778547, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trials\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"late June\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"any real idea\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At least the trials would be at Hayward Field, where two of Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s uncles had starred.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"Hayward Field\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"uncles\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s home field, site of his first Junior Olympics, first national championship and other indelible moments.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s home field\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"his first Junior Olympics\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"first national championship\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"other indelible moments\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But had the injury healed enough to even compete?\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injury\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Had it healed enough to make the national team?\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the national team\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enough to train an additional six weeks afterward to prepare for Paris?\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999432097576819, \"rank\": 5.679346748888838e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The afternoon after he injured his pec, Ryan called his father.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2289, \"end\": 2293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9981267081859916, \"rank\": 0.0017889617618315704, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his pec\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained the injury, the pain, the doubts.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injury\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"the doubts\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Ryan hung up, Mitch heard him say he wanted to be alone.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9981267081859916, \"rank\": 0.0017889617618315704, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 2377, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999825266629405, \"rank\": 1.7395965820502854e-05, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He needed to process this.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One morning, he was preparing to seize another gold.\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another gold\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That night, he was wondering if his career was finished.\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But process it he did.\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day, unable to find Ryan, one of his training partners went to the place he knew he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d be\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cshop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d where they lift weights.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9981267081859916, \"rank\": 0.0017889617618315704, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his training partners\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2677}, {\"ngram\": \"weights\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There he was:pumping iron.\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"iron\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had figured out a way to do that without risking further damage to the elbow or the pec muscle.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"further damage\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"the elbow\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"the pec muscle\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan Crouser figures stuff out.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2850, \"end\": 2862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Crouser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the University of Texas, he loved economics and engineering classes, and he obtained a Master\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s in finance.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"Texas\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"economics and engineering classes\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"a Master\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"finance\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He generally approaches life like a personal science experiment.\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3023}, {\"ngram\": \"a personal science experiment\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning his first gold medal, in Rio, Ryan wanted to throw farther, as far as humanly possible.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3100, \"end\": 3103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9852661818577871, \"rank\": 0.014948685963652286, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 3105, \"end\": 3109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9993925401648164, \"rank\": 0.000594075348838333, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first gold medal\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, he sought microscopic advances: in nutrition, sleep and training techniques.\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"microscopic advances\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3197}, {\"ngram\": \"nutrition\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"techniques\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such analytical drive runs in the family.\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Such analytical drive runs\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To call the Crousers a family of throwers doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t quite capture the depth of their collective involvement in the throwing disciplines.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Crousers\", \"from\": 3295, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"throwers\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"the depth\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"their collective involvement\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"the throwing disciplines\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Long before Ryan was around,Sports Illustrateddispatched its legendary track writer, Kenny Moore, to Boring, Ore., to profile Mitch, his brother Dean and their younger brother, Brian, in 1983.\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3436, \"end\": 3440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9993925401648164, \"rank\": 0.000594075348838333, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 3509, \"end\": 3520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Moore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.767409323260426e-15, \"text\": \"Kenny Moore\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5