\"Larry\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3710}, {\"ngram\": \"the family patriarch\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He never pushed any of his children into throwing, but one day he brought home a barbell and issued a challenge: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIf you can clean-and-jerk 40 pounds, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll buy you a shot.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The boys met the challenge and Larry made good on his promise.\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his children\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3774}, {\"ngram\": \"throwing\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3788}, {\"ngram\": \"a barbell\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3827}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3850}, {\"ngram\": \"clean-and-jerk 40 pounds\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"a shot.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The boys\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3926}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"Larry\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"his promise\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They took turns throwing the shot all over a vacant lot next door.\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 4048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"turns\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 3997}, {\"ngram\": \"the shot\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4015}, {\"ngram\": \"a vacant lot\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If they made 50 proper throws, Larry would get them a discus.\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"50 proper throws\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4078}, {\"ngram\": \"Larry\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4085}, {\"ngram\": \"a discus\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If they did the same with the discus, he would get them what Dean calls the Holy Grail of throwing objects\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094ajavelin.\", \"from\": 4111, \"to\": 4229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4172, \"end\": 4176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/