"to\": 4374}, {\"ngram\": \"shot\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, 61, competed in two Olympics in the javelin.\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brian\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4391}, {\"ngram\": \"two Olympics\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4421}, {\"ngram\": \"the javelin\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eventually, the brothers started a business training athletes; initially, as wholesale distributors, selling nutrition plans, athletic equipment and training regimens.\", \"from\": 4439, \"to\": 4606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the brothers\", \"from\": 4451, \"to\": 4463}, {\"ngram\": \"a business training athletes\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4500}, {\"ngram\": \"wholesale distributors\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4538}, {\"ngram\": \"nutrition plans\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4563}, {\"ngram\": \"athletic equipment and training regimens\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had a barn and they put up a large, industrial-strength, commercial-grade net, purchased at a nearby Army surplus store, the kind used to lower soldiers from helicopters (i.e.,Crouserstrong), for their pupils to throw into.\", \"from\": 4607, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4713, \"end\": 4731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surplus_store\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Army surplus store\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surplus_store\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surplus_store\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a barn\", \"from\": 4616, \"to\": 4622}, {\"ngram\": \"a large, industrial-strength, commercial-grade net\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4689}, {\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 4733, \"to\": 4741}, {\"ngram\": \"soldiers\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4764}, {\"ngram\": \"helicopters\", \"from\": 4770, \"to\": 4781}, {\"ngram\": \"their pupils\", \"from\": 4808, \"to\": 4820}]}, {